text: Terres-de-Caux is a commune in the department of Seine-Maritime, northern France. The municipality was established on 1 January 2017 by merger of the former communes of Fauville-en-Caux (the seat), Auzouville-Auberbosc, Bennetot, Bermonville, Ricarville, Sainte-Marguerite-sur-Fauville and Saint- Pierre-Lavis.Arrêté préfectoral 12 September 2016 == See also == *Communes of the Seine-Maritime department == References == Category:Communes of Seine- Maritime
title: Terres-de-Caux
